      "text": "And I know it's not bad to dream a little bit, dream with me.",
      "start": 90.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 98.77999877929688,
      "text": "I know it gets savage sometimes, you know.",
      "start": 96.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 103.54000091552734,
      "text": "You see that girl you want and she's like nah, nah, nah, nah, nah, nah, nah, not today.",
      "start": 98.87999725341797
    },
    {
