      "text": "Gets a little rough, but you dress yourself up, come back tough.",
      "start": 103.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 112.91999816894531,
      "text": "That's right, because there's a different person waiting for you.",
      "start": 109.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 115.45999908447266,
      "text": "It's all about the soul, and it's all about the challenge.",
